      <h2>About Me</h2>
      <p>
        I am Wayne Mandila, a passionate aeronautical engineer and tech enthusiast. Currently pursuing my degree at the Technical University of Kenya, I specialize in UAV development, robotics, and algorithm-driven systems. My journey began with a curiosity about flight mechanics, and it has evolved into a quest to redefine how we interact with aerospace technologies.
      </p>
      <p>
        With a blend of creativity and technical expertise, I have successfully worked on projects like radar systems and drone swarming algorithms. I constantly seek opportunities to merge aeronautics, automation, and machine learning to solve real-world challenges.
      </p>
